<h1>Kid Smoothie</h1>
<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
<li>1 cup plain kefir</li>
<li>1 frozen banana</li>
<li>1/2 cup frozen blueberries</li>
<li>1/2 cup frozen mango</li>
<li>1/2 cup baby spinach</li>
<li>1 tablespoon hemp seeds (or chia seeds)</li>
<li>1 tablespoon avocado (optional)</li>
</ul>
<h2>Steps</h2>
<ol>
<li>Blend all ingredients in a high-powered blender.</li>
<li>Enjoy.</li>
</ol>
